Hi Ron,

Thanks for writing to Dr Math.  There are 10,000 codes, including all
of the numbers from

  0000
  0001
  0002
  0003

on up to

  9999.

If you have any questions about this or need more help, please write
back, and I will try to offer further suggestions.

